  "prompt": "What are the recipes of five minutes easy to make snacks?",
  "response": "Here are some easy snack recipes that can be prepared in about five minutes:\n\n### 1. **Peanut Butter Banana Toast**\n**Ingredients:**\n- Whole grain bread\n- Peanut butter\n- Banana\n- Honey (optional)\n- Cinnamon (optional)\n\n**Instructions:**\n1. Toast a slice of whole grain bread.\n2. Spread a generous layer of peanut butter on the toast.\n3. Slice a banana and arrange the slices on top of the peanut butter.\n4. Drizzle with honey and sprinkle with cinnamon if desired.\n\n### 2. **Yogurt Parfait**\n**Ingredients:**\n- Greek yogurt\n- Granola\n- Fresh berries (strawberries, blueberries, raspberries)\n\n**Instructions:**\n1. In a cup or bowl, add a layer of Greek yogurt.\n2. Add a layer of granola on top of the yogurt.\n3. Top with fresh berries.\n4. Repeat layers if desired and enjoy!\n\n### 3. **Caprese Skewers**\n**Ingredients:**\n- Cherry tomatoes\n- Fresh mozzarella balls\n- Fresh basil leaves\n- Balsamic glaze (optional)\n- Salt and pepper\n\n**Instructions:**\n1. On a toothpick or small skewer, thread a cherry tomato, a basil leaf, and a mozzarella ball.\n2. Repeat until all ingredients are used up.\n3. Drizzle with balsamic glaze and sprinkle with salt and pepper if desired.\n\n### 4. **Avocado Toast**\n**Ingredients:**\n- Whole grain bread\n- Ripe avocado\n- Salt and pepper\n- Red pepper flakes (optional)\n- Lemon juice (optional)\n\n**Instructions:**\n1. Toast a slice of whole grain bread.\n2. While the bread is toasting, mash a ripe avocado in a bowl.\n3. Spread the mashed avocado on the toast.\n4. Season with salt, pepper, and red pepper flakes or a squeeze of lemon juice if you like.\n\n### 5. **Cucumber and Hummus Bites**\n**Ingredients:**\n- Cucumber\n- Hummus\n- Cherry tomatoes (optional)\n- Olive oil (optional)\n\n**Instructions:**\n1. Slice the cucumber into thick rounds.\n2. Top each cucumber slice with a dollop of hummus.\n3. Add a halved cherry tomato on top of the hummus for extra flavor, if desired.\n4. Drizzle with olive oil for added richness, if you like.\n\nThese snacks are quick, delicious, and can be customized based on your preferences! Enjoy!",
